{"word":"Johanan","slug":"johanan","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Johanan</b> <a href=\"#/H3110\">H3110</a> <br/> 1. A Jewish captain<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=25&verse=24'>2Ki 25:24</a> <br/> - Warns Gedaliah against Ishmael<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=40&verse=16'>Jer 40:16</a> <br/> - Ishmael defeated by<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=41&verse=15'>Jer 41:15</a> <br/> - Sought prayers of Jeremiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=42&verse=3'>Jer 42:3</a> <br/> - Disobeyed Jeremiah and took him to Egypt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=43&verse=7'>Jer 43:7</a> <br/> 2. Son of Josiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=3&verse=15'>1Ch 3:15</a><br/> 3. A son of Elioenai<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=3&verse=24'>1Ch 3:24</a><br/> 4. A Levite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=10'>1Ch 6:10</a><br/> 5. Two Israelites who joined David at Ziklag<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=12&verse=4'>1Ch 12:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=12&verse=12'>1Ch 12:12</a><br/> 6. An Ephraimite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=28&verse=12'>2Ch 28:12</a><br/> 7. A returned exile<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=8&verse=12'>Ezr 8:12</a><br/> 8. A priest<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=6'>Ezr 10:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=23'>Neh 12:23</a> <br/> - Probably identical with Jonathan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=11'>Neh 12:11</a> <br/> 9. Son of Tobiah the Ammonite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=6&verse=18'>Neh 6:18</a>"}]}